Aries.decription: Aries is bold and ambitious, dives headfirst into even the most challenging situations. Aries loves to be number one. Aries is a passionate, motivated, and confident leader who builds community with their cheerful disposition and relentless determination.

Taurus.decription: Represented by the bull, Taurus is an earth sign. Taureans loves relaxing in peace, rural environments surrounded by soft sounds, soothing aromas, and succulent flavors. At the same time, Taurus are not afraid to work hard for their goals.
